accused Mitchelson of rape, is pending. The two women's allegations
were the subject of a recent ``60 Minutes'' program.
   Mitchelson has represented such clients as actress Joan Collins;
he was the lawyer in a landmark ``palimony'' case brought by the
live-in girlfriend of the late actor Lee Marvin.
